title: Mens Health Coach MagBook Issue 10 - 2014  AU
description:
Men's Health Coach MagBook Issue 10 - 2014  AU

132 Pages | True PDF | English | 19 MB 


A new quarterly title from the editors of Men's Health.  Following the success of Australian Men's Health, Coach is the new single subject resource for the ambitious, active man. Presented in an entertaining, informative question-and-answer format, Coach covers such diverse subjects as muscle, weight loss, cardio fitness and nutrition. As the tagline says, Coach is Personal Training for Men.
